<button aria-label="Toggle AAC usage analytics" style="background:none;border:none;padding:0;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;width:100%;text-align:left;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#374151;margin-bottom:0">📊 AAC Usage Analytics <span style="color:#6b7280;font-weight:400;margin-left:auto;font-size:10px">▼ show</span>
</button>
